@0 = ~The Duke's have proclaimed that <CHARNAME>, hero of Baldur's Gate, was innocent after all. Word is <PRO_HESHE> may be coming back to the city. That would be something, wouldn't it?~
@1 = ~Been hearing that there's trouble brewing far to the southeast. It's said that Fire Giants are gathering outside of one of the Tethyrian cities... Saradush, I think it was.~
@2 = ~温斯顿勋爵在清理凯拉的圣战军难民方面做得很棒，不是吗？~
@3 = ~这事你可别告诉别人，但有消息说银盾公爵的女儿还没有完全从她的遭遇中恢复过来。~
@4 = ~有传言说<CHARNAME>，博德之门的英雄，和焰拳的一名军官有奸——擦出了火花。~
@5 = ~Things've finally settled down after the iron shortages, the crusade, and the refugee crisis. We could all do with some peace and quiet for a change, aye?~